---
title: Sweet and Savoury Pork Burgers with Herby Fries, Dijonnaise and Maple Ketchup
description: Everyone loves a good hamburger, but this one may just change the game! Maple and thyme make pork shine here, while feeling the love from savoury Dijonnaise and a delectable maple ketchup. Throw in a fresh apple-spinach salad and some herby potato wedges, and this dish may just have you second-guessing that classic beef burger next time you have the craving!
